<lyrics>[V1]
 yạ rạfʿạaⁿ ʿny kẖṭyty yạ sndy fy wḥdty
 yạ qạỷdy ltwbty yạ mrsẖdy wṣkẖrty
 mn gẖyrk ly qwty whạdyạ fy ḥyrty
 yạ nṣrty rby fy mḥnty yạ mljạ̉y fy ḍyqty
 yạ mạsḥạaⁿ ly dmʿty yạ mstjyb ṭlbty
 mn gẖyrk ly qwty whạdyạ fy ḥyrty
 yạ ḥạrsy dwmạaⁿ fy kẖṭwty nʿmtk ly qwty
 trnymty ạ̉nsẖwdty ạhdy lk mḥbty
 mn gẖyrk ly qwty whạdyạ fy ḥyrty
 ạ̉nt ạ̹lhy mạlky sẖkry lk .ʿbạdty fạqbl trnymty</lyrics>
<title>yạ rạfʿaⁿạ</title>
</song>